AMIGO TECHNOLOGY June Sales Fall 12.27% (Table) : 6241 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-08T17:25:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/amigo-technology-june-sales-fall-12-27-table-6241-tt.html
AMIGO TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 12.27% to NT$12,381,000 from NT$14,113,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             12,381           14,113    
YOY%             -12.27%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            126,132          138,891    
YOY%              -9.19% 
=================================================================
 